    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ミクと月のテンペストのライブ終了後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、本当に頑張ったな\nライブ大盛況だったぞ、さすがだよ",
      "startTime": 5.1666669846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　ミクちゃんの記念日を\n私達の歌でお祝い出来て良かったです",
      "startTime": 11.5730643034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのおかげで、本当に素敵な日になったよ！",
      "startTime": 14.633650883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "提案なんだけど、もっと素敵な日にするのはどうかな？\n打ち上げがわりに、みんなでまたお祭りに行こうよ！",
      "startTime": 24.2666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "賛成さんせーい！　屋台たっくさん巡っちゃおー\n今日はどーんなお店が並んでるかな～",
      "startTime": 33.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "日によって屋台の内容が変わるみたいだし\n面白い遊びが出来る屋台を探しに行くのもいいかも！",
      "startTime": 39.7666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "屋台っていろいろあるの？",
      "startTime": 43.757227079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん。いろいろあるよ\n遊びなら、金魚すくいにヨーヨー釣り……",
      "startTime": 49.4999986649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "輪投げにくじ引きからダーツまで！\nミクちゃんが知らない屋台はまだまだあるんだよ",
      "startTime": 56.2333319982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ご飯が食べれる屋台だってすーっごく一杯あるんだよー\nチュロスとか、クロワッサンたい焼きとか！",
      "startTime": 64.3666666825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだー！\nわくわく！",
      "startTime": 69.4999986649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ミクも乗り気みたいだし、早速行くか\nまだまだお祭りは、やってるみたいだしな",
      "startTime": 74.999999555,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4164.057294199992,
          "startTime": 79.1640568492
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "見て、ミクちゃん！\n前に来た時より、屋台沢山あるよー！",
      "startTime": 81.7640569366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、楽しそうだね\nすずちゃんなんか、一目散に走って行っちゃったし",
      "startTime": 88.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、はしゃぎ過ぎじゃないのか……？\nまぁ、沙季と琴乃がついて行ったし大丈夫だろう",
      "startTime": 95.933330981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺達は俺達で祭りを楽しむとするか\nミクにもいろんな屋台を見てほしいしな",
      "startTime": 103.3666643143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "楽しかったねー！　射的でクッション、ゲット出来たし\nでも芽衣、そろそろお腹ペコペコで限界かも～",
      "startTime": 114.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "夢中で遊んでたから気が付かなかったけど\n私もお腹減ってきちゃったな……何かないかな？",
      "startTime": 122.7666668575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、見て！\nリンゴ飴！",
      "startTime": 130.1000020982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ん……？　こっちのリンゴ飴にはココアパウダーが\nこっちにはシナモンパウダーがまぶしてあるのか？",
      "startTime": 136.1333369096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、最近はいろんな味があるんだよ\nカラフルで綺麗だから、SNSでも話題なんだー",
      "startTime": 142.8792888319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "チョコチップやキャラメルでコーティングされていて\n普通のリンゴ飴とはまた違った味がするんだよね",
      "startTime": 150.0000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことになってるんだな、全然知らなかったよ\nミクも、よく見つけたな。早速買おうか",
      "startTime": 158.2666687649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "いただきまーす！　あ～ん……\nんーー！　外はカリカリ、中はジューシ～！",
      "startTime": 169.1666617711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "確かに美味しいが……ぽろぽろ崩れて……\nうっ、チョコが服についてしまった……",
      "startTime": 180.733333985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "動かないで下さい、ウェットティッシュ持ってるので\nんー、でもこれは……色が残っちゃうかもしれませんね",
      "startTime": 189.1333323797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_03_01-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "あわわ、大変……",
      "startTime": 196.0408351654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
